Subject: Rope Class: Rope with Toga
Description: Interested in rope play? This class will provide information on basic skills, practical application, and safety and consent mechanics involved in rope bondage. You'll see demonstrations, and receive hands on lessons. We'll cover rope suspension safety and techniques, types of rope and their different applications, rope top techniques, and skills.This event is 18+.
